	   <tr><td colspan=2>i have just made a barbarian shammy and have made some mistakes it seems.....<br>i put something like, 10 in wisdom 10 in charisma ( i thought charm was gonna be very important) and 5 in stamina.<br>Everyone says to put all (or at least 20) in wisdom. This wouldn't be a problem as i could just delete it and start again. The problem is i am level&nbsp;&nbsp;now and some generous guy has given me: a runed totem staff, 8pp, a langseax (to sell) rusty spiked shoulder pads and a cutthroat ring.<br>I dont wanna just waste all that stuff<br><br>Should i restart or not? <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
