	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is the most efficient method for a shaman to solo at levels 24+.&nbsp;&nbsp;DOTs are the most mana efficient damage spells the shaman gets, and by rooting the mob you ensure that they take full damage from the DOT.  You can also slow the mob and haste yourself and melee the mob while doted and root if you get hurt to much.  Do this to keep your offence, defence and melee skills maxed for your level.  Since there is a message when your DOT wears off, just reapply it and re apply root, and you can sit and meditate or do the shaman dance (meditate and canibalize) while your DOT kills the mob.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
